他们找到的证据有87%是支持自己原本立场的
87 percent of the evidence they find supports their original stance

212
00:06:38,733 --> 00:06:40,133
不是AI偏心
It is not that AI is biased

213
00:06:40,266 --> 00:06:41,233
是你偏心
You are the biased one

214
00:06:41,366 --> 00:06:44,000
AI只是在忠实地回答你的问题
AI is just faithfully answering your questions

215
00:06:44,133 --> 00:06:46,433
但你的问题本身就是偏的
But your questions themselves are biased

216
00:06:46,566 --> 00:06:48,833
你现在打开你的AI聊天记录
Open your AI chat history now

217
00:06:48,966 --> 00:06:50,833
翻翻你最近问的那些问题
Look through the questions you asked recently

218
00:06:51,166 --> 00:06:52,233
你有没有发现
Have you noticed

219
00:06:52,766 --> 00:06:54,333
你问问题的方式
The way you ask questions

220
00:06:54,333 --> 00:06:56,100
已经在替你做决定了
Is already making decisions for you

221
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:58,633
这个偏差在专业领域更致命
This bias is even more deadly in professional fields

