00:07:11,833 --> 00:07:13,333
当不一致时
When they disagreed

228
00:07:13,333 --> 00:07:15,966
医生改变自己判断的概率
The probability of doctors changing their own judgment

229
00:07:16,166 --> 00:07:18,800
远远高于改变AI判断的概率
Was far higher than changing the AI judgment

230
00:07:18,966 --> 00:07:19,800
换句话说
In other words

231
00:07:19,833 --> 00:07:22,600
医生不是在用AI做更好的诊断
Doctors were not using AI to make better diagnoses

232
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:25,700
他们是在用AI给自己的直觉盖章
They were using AI to rubber stamp their own intuition

233
00:07:25,866 --> 00:07:27,100
更可怕的是
What is even scarier

234
00:07:27,633 --> 00:07:29,533
AI不一定是对的
AI is not necessarily right

235
00:07:29,666 --> 00:07:33,566
ChatGPT曾经信誓旦旦地编造了不存在的学术论文
ChatGPT once confidently fabricated non existent academic papers

236
00:07:33,666 --> 00:07:35,333
虚构的历史事件
Made up historical events

237
00:07:35,333 --> 00:07:37,233
甚至编造了不存在的人
Even invented people who do not exist

238
00:07:37,433 --> 00:07:38,966
它叫AI幻觉
This is called AI hallucination

239
00:07:39,166 --> 00:07:40,966
但因为它说得太自信了
But because it sounds so confident

240
00:07:41,466 --> 00:07:42,666
排版整齐
Perfectly formatted

241
00:07:42,666 --> 00:07:43,800
引文规范
Properly cited

242
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,033
语气坚定
Firm tone

243
00:07:45,533 --> 00:07:48,266
你的确认偏误加上自动化偏见
Your confirmation bias plus automation bias

244
00:07:48,266 --> 00:07:50,233
让你根本不会怀疑它
Makes you not doubt it at all

245
00:07:50,433 --> 00:07:51,566
AI给你答案
AI gives you an answer

246
