其实你只是在给自己的偏见找了一个更有说服力的复读机
Actually you are just finding a more convincing parrot for your own biases

249
00:07:58,300 --> 00:07:59,000
好
OK

250
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,800
前面讲了锚定和确认
We covered anchoring and confirmation

