254
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,633
1981年
In 1981

255
00:08:07,633 --> 00:08:12,000
卡尼曼和特沃斯基做了心理学史上最著名的实验之一
Kahneman and Tversky conducted one of the most famous experiments in psychology history

256
00:08:12,133 --> 00:08:14,200
