They told two groups of doctors the same fact

257
00:08:14,333 --> 00:08:16,100
一种手术的存活率是90%
A surgery has a 90 percent survival rate

258
00:08:16,666 --> 00:08:18,733
但他们对第一组医生说
But they told the first group of doctors

259
00:08:19,266 --> 00:08:21,133
这个手术的存活率是90%
The survival rate of this surgery is 90 percent

260
00:08:21,666 --> 00:08:23,066
对第二组医生说
They told the second group of doctors

261
00:08:23,066 --> 00:08:25,100
这个手术的死亡率是10%
The mortality rate of this surgery is 10 percent

262
00:08:25,633 --> 00:08:26,433
结果
The result

263
00:08:27,166 --> 00:08:30,500
听到存活率90%的医生
Doctors who heard 90 percent survival rate

264
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:33,100
有84%推荐这个手术
84 percent recommended this surgery

265
00:08:33,233 --> 00:08:35,333
听到死亡率10%的医生
Doctors who heard 10 percent mortality rate

266
00:08:35,566 --> 00:08:37,500
只有50%推荐
Only 50 percent recommended it

267
00:08:37,633 --> 00:08:38,766
同一个事实
The same fact

268
00:08:38,833 --> 00:08:40,766
两组数据一模一样
Two identical sets of data

269
00:08:40,766 --> 00:08:42,300
只是换了个说法
Just phrased differently

270
00:08:42,366 --> 00:08:44,333
推荐率差了34个百分点
The recommendation rate differed by 34 percentage points

271
00:08:44,433 --> 00:08:46,633
人不是在根据事实做决定
People do not make decisions based on facts

272
00:08:46,666 --> 00:08:49,366
人是在根据事实的包装方式做决定
People make decisions based on how facts are packaged

273
00:08:49,533 --> 00:08:50,333
现在
Now

274
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:53,400
这个效应被AI放大了无数倍
This effect has been amplified countless times by AI

275
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,500
你问AI
You ask AI

276
