历史年化收益8%
Historical annualized return of 8 percent

279
00:08:59,033 --> 00:09:01,000
同期银行存款利率2%
Bank deposit rate in the same period is 2 percent

280
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,200
你一听
You hear that

281
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:03,600
8%
8 percent

282
