但你再问一遍
But ask again

284
00:09:06,366 --> 00:09:07,800
这个产品有风险吗
Does this product have risks

285
00:09:07,833 --> 00:09:08,466
AI说
AI says

286
00:09:08,466 --> 00:09:10,333
过去三年最大回撤25%
Maximum drawdown of 25 percent over the past three years

287
00:09:10,566 --> 00:09:13,333
42%的投资者出现过亏损
42 percent of investors experienced losses

288
00:09:13,466 --> 00:09:14,433
同一个产品
The same product

289
00:09:14,433 --> 00:09:15,400
两种说法
Two different ways to describe it

290
00:09:15,566 --> 00:09:16,533
你选哪个
Which one do you choose

291
00:09:16,666 --> 00:09:20,533
大部分人在听到第一种描述的时候倾向于买入
Most people tend to buy when they hear the first description

292
00:09:20,966 --> 00:09:23,566
听到第二种描述的时候倾向于放弃
And tend to give up when they hear the second description

293
00:09:23,633 --> 00:09:26,300
但真正的问题不在于AI在帮你分析
But the real problem is not that AI is helping you analyze

294
00:09:26,433 --> 00:09:28,300
它确实给了你真实的数据
It did give you real data

295
00:09:28,433 --> 00:09:29,366
问题是
The problem is

296
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:31,666
AI在回答你的那一刻
At the moment AI answers you

297
00:09:31,666 --> 00:09:33,500
已经帮你选了框架
It has already chosen a frame for you

298
00:09:33,633 --> 00:09:35,233
你问AI该不该做
You ask AI whether you should do it

299
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:37,400
它会从做的理由开始分析
It will start analyzing reasons to do it

300
