你问AI有什么风险
You ask AI what the risks are

301
00:09:39,433 --> 00:09:41,800
它会从不做的好处开始分析
It will start analyzing the benefits of not doing it

302
00:09:41,933 --> 00:09:45,200
你的提问方式决定了AI的回答框架
The way you ask determines AIs response frame

303
00:09:45,566 --> 00:09:48,533
AI的回答框架决定了你的最终选择
AIs response frame determines your final choice

304
