大多数创业者即使失败了
Most entrepreneurs even if they fail

317
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:16,366
也找到了更好的工作
Still found better jobs

318
00:10:16,366 --> 00:10:18,033
积累了人脉和经验
Built networks and experience

319
00:10:18,366 --> 00:10:20,400
收入最终超过了之前
And eventually earned more than before

320
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,800
同一个决定
The same decision

321
00:10:21,966 --> 00:10:23,166
换一种问法
Asked differently

322
00:10:23,233 --> 00:10:25,333
你的人生走向可能完全不同
Your life trajectory could be completely different

323
00:10:25,466 --> 00:10:28,433
而你甚至不知道自己只看到了真相的一半
And you do not even know you only saw half the truth

324
00:10:28,733 --> 00:10:30,000
三个偏差讲完了
Three biases covered

325
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,000
锚定
Anchoring

326
00:10:31,133 --> 00:10:32,266
确认偏误
Confirmation bias

327
