336
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:51,733
你被框架效应操纵了
You are manipulated by the framing effect

337
00:10:51,866 --> 00:10:52,966
三重暴击
A triple blow

338
00:10:53,166 --> 00:10:55,366
但你先别急着卸载ChatGPT
But do not rush to uninstall ChatGPT just yet

339
00:10:55,566 --> 00:10:56,833
AI不是敌人
AI is not the enemy

340
